{"tid":1822310,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]到底點樣可以細心啲T^T真心喊出黎","createTime":"2020-01-13T01:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T10:34:32.000Z","uid":331286,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"97ae1d4bcf6c9c9444b1371bc4a0415059556ebd","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"出黎做野就兩年<br />\n個人依然超級大頭蝦<br />\n就岩岩<br />\n我發現有件貼紙我已經印咗3次錯咗3次<br />\n然後第四轉一陣就要交俾客時<br />\n我發現仲係錯緊<br />\n係我出file錯咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大都粗心大細<br />\n一直都無咩大問題<br />\n無諗過改<br />\n但今次真係大鑊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為個客係新長line<br />\n係多job跟並且長做長有既大客<br />\n老細好緊張<br />\n如果我搞到佢個客無咗<br />\n自殺都搞唔掂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次錯應該無咩大問題<br />\n因為我可以後補個張<br />\n最大問題係老細居然將個客交俾我跟<br />\n我咁大頭蝦真係遲早出事<br />\n我依家真係驚到瀨<br />\n好大壓力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到底點先可改善</span></strong></span><br />\n求打救"},{"pid":"f3580318a5ab1bd011e0592251f7ba74f8edfdc6","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"平時已經多甩漏<br />\n我係老細我都想揑死自己<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解老細要俾我跟呢個大客<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係唔明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262e6762b74644c1fa63f4482559a68808a01850","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1124d6ff9317f0eb4d58f6df437db37c44dc887c","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bd66898f68d8953e80eb25096e17763e7b644c","tid":1822310,"uid":284901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"我都覺得自己不夠細心, 唯有檢查多兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1886b5c48c3c790f07553ef7e0906cd2904bb8f","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c66bbdfb3ae8e3b5667514d82221b1a57272d25","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T01:37:46.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d847829c92dde9f29c5206c9cf4ccdd8c5db4","tid":1822310,"uid":331286,"like":0,